# MAIL ULB #

IMAPAccount ULB
Host imap.ULB.ac.be
Port 993
User bedumont
PassCmd "pass Email/ulb.ac.be/bedumont"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore ULB-remote
Account ULB

MaildirStore ULB-local
Path ~/Mail/ULB/
Inbox ~/Mail/ULB/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel ULB
Master :ULB-remote:
Slave :ULB-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *


